    "causal_summary": "Phase 1 shipped the new `/doctor` router additively. That left the repository in an intentional temporary overlap: the final design wants 3 markdown command entrypoints (`doctor.md`, `doctor/mcp.md`, `doctor/update.md`), but Phase 1 kept the 9 old per-target markdown files in place so validation could compare old and new behavior. The old surface also exists in runtime mirrors: `.claude/commands/doctor/` auto-syncs from `.opencode/commands/doctor/`, `.codex/prompts` symlinks to `.opencode/commands`, and `.gemini/commands/doctor/*.toml` is independent.",
